# Park Dental Clinic - Internal Link Structure & Navigation Recommendations

## Current Problem

The site is a single-page application (SPA) with all content on one URL (`/`). Navigation uses anchor links (`#home`, `#clinic`, `#services`, `#testimonials`, `#team`, `#contact`) that scroll to sections on the same page. There are zero separate page URLs.

This causes two major problems:
1. **GEO audit scored 0/15 on crawlable internal links** - AI crawlers and search engines see only one URL with no link graph to follow
2. **No page-level SEO** - Each dental service (implants, cosmetic, root canal, etc.) should have its own indexable page targeting specific search keywords like "dental implants in Kochi" or "root canal treatment Kerala"

## Recommended Architecture

### Phase 1: Create Service Pages (Highest Priority)

Split the current single-page site into separate pages. Each service gets its own URL with dedicated content.

