|------|-----|----------------|----------|
| Homepage | `/` | dentist kochi, dental clinic kerala | 1.0 |
| Dental Implants | `/dental-implants` | dental implants kochi, tooth implant kerala, all-on-4 kochi | 0.9 |
| Cosmetic Dentistry | `/cosmetic-dentistry` | cosmetic dentist kochi, veneers kerala, smile makeover | 0.9 |
| Root Canal | `/root-canal-treatment` | root canal kochi, RCT kerala, painless root canal | 0.8 |
| Teeth Whitening | `/teeth-whitening` | teeth whitening kochi, laser whitening kerala | 0.8 |
