## Implementation Notes

- The site is built by whyweb.in. Share this document with them as the development spec.
- If the site uses a framework like React or Vue, ensure the new pages use server-side rendering (SSR) or static generation (SSG). The current SPA approach means crawlers only see one page.
- The booking modal (`#booking-modal`) can remain as a modal on each page. It does not need its own URL.
- Keep the Google Maps link (`https://maps.app.goo.gl/oPA1jHT1RMKtVsqB9`) on the contact page and homepage footer.
- Update the `og:url` meta tag from `https://parkdentalclinic.in` to `https://www.parkdentalclinics.co.in/` - it currently points to a different domain.
